{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be dynamic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Sterling & Stone Legal</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #1f3a93; /* Deep Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #3b5998; /* Slightly lighter blue */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --heading-color: #ffffff;\n            --body-color: #f4f4f4;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--body-color);\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #e8491d 3px solid;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 28px;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            color: var(--heading-color);\n        }\n\n        header nav {\n            display: flex;\n        }\n\n        header ul {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            list-style: none;\n        }\n\n        header li {\n            display: inline;\n            margin-left: 20px;\n        }\n\n        header a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            padding: 5px 10px;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        header a:hover {\n            color: #cccccc;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            min-height: 400px;\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x400/1f3a93/ffffff?text=Sterling+%26+Stone+Legal') no-repeat 0 -100px;\n            background-size: cover;\n            background-position: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(31, 58, 147, 0.7); /* Overlay with primary color */\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 48px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--heading-color);\n            z-index: 1;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 20px;\n            z-index: 1;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        #services, #about, #contact {\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #services h3, #about h3, #contact h3 {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item, .team-member {\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 30%;\n            margin: 1.5%;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background: #fff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            vertical-align: top;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover, .team-member:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h4 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 22px;\n        }\n\n        .team-member img {\n            width: 150px;\n            height: 150px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .team-member h4 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-size: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .team-member p {\n            font-style: italic;\n            color: #555;\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n\n        #contact form {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            display: inline-block;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        #contact label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            color: #333;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Important */\n            font-size: 16px;\n        }\n\n        #contact textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        #contact button {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            transition: background 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Sterling & Stone Legal</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#services\">Services</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Your Trusted Legal Partners</h2>\n            <p>Dedicated to providing exceptional legal counsel and representation.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"main-content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <section id=\"about\">\n                <h3>About Us</h3>\n                <p>Sterling & Stone Legal is a distinguished law firm committed to delivering high-quality legal services with integrity and expertise. Our team of seasoned attorneys brings a wealth of experience across various practice areas, ensuring our clients receive tailored and effective solutions. We pride ourselves on building strong, lasting relationships based on trust and mutual respect.</p>\n                <div class=\"team-member\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150/1f3a93/ffffff?text=JS\" alt=\"John Sterling\">\n                    <h4>John Sterling</h4>\n                    <p>Senior Partner</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"team-member\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150/3b5998/ffffff?text=AS\" alt=\"Alice Stone\">\n                    <h4>Alice Stone</h4>\n                    <p>Managing Partner</p>\n                </div>\n            </section>\n\n            <section id=\"services\">\n                <h3>Our Services</h3>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Corporate Law</h4>\n                    <p>Navigating complex business regulations and transactions with precision.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Litigation</h4>\n                    <p>Aggressive and strategic representation in all types of disputes.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Real Estate Law</h4>\n                    <p>Expert guidance for property transactions and development.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Family Law</h4>\n                    <p>Compassionate and effective support for family matters.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Estate Planning</h4>\n                    <p>Securing your legacy and protecting your loved ones.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Intellectual Property</h4>\n                    <p>Safeguarding your innovations and creative works.</p>\n                </div>\n            </section>\n\n            <section id=\"contact\">\n                <h3>Contact Us</h3>\n                <p>We are ready to assist you. Please reach out to schedule a consultation.</p>\n                <form id=\"contact-form\">\n                    <div>\n                        <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                        <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                        <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                        <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                        <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                        <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" required></textarea>\n                    </div>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </section>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Sterling & Stone Legal. All Rights Reserved.</p>\n            <p><a href=\"mailto:info@sterlingstonelaw.com\">info@sterlingstonelaw.com</a> | (123) 456-7890</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch shortly.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}